CatDescriptText: David Leo Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh from 1946 to 1959, and Governor of Pennsylvania from 1959 to 1963.  He died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of eight men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence seated at desk, signing document, gathered in the Office of the Mayor at the City County Building
